import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  

export default class MDXContent extends React.Component {
  constructor(props) {
    super(props)
    this.layout = null
  }
  render() {
    const { components, ...props } = this.props

    return <MDXTag
             name="wrapper"
             
             components={components}><MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"seo-for-beginners"}}>{`SEO For Beginners`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"keywords"}}>{`Keywords`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Use the Keywords Everywhere plugin to find out volume, cost-per-click and competition for certain keywords.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`The shorter the phrase, the higher the cost and competition. The longer the phrase, the less search frequency.`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"on-page-optimisation"}}>{`On Page Optimisation`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="p" components={components}>{`How can we optimise our home page?`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Update the image and description to include these keywords.`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Update the "keywords" meta tag `}<MDXTag name="inlineCode" components={components} parentName="li">{`<meta name="keywords" content="Dennis,O'Keeffe,Blog,Sydney,Developer,Official,Software" />`}</MDXTag></MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="h2" components={components} props={{"id":"seo-for-business"}}>{`SEO for business`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="ul" components={components}>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Google MyBusiness`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Yelp business`}</MDXTag>
<MDXTag name="li" components={components} parentName="ul">{`Trip Advisor`}</MDXTag>
</MDXTag>
           </MDXTag>
  }
}
